---
title: Eggplant and Sun-Dried Tomato Linguine
description: Eggplant, mozzarella, and tomato sauce are a true trifecta of Italian cuisine. The mere mention of the combo is enough to make anyone weak in the knees. So tossing it with strands of al dente linguine seemed like a no-brainer to us, especially with the addition of sun-dried tomato to the sauce, which add bursts of tangy flavor throughout.
